{"tid":1378952,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 中共下一步點反擊","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:39:23.000Z","uid":285794,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ddb28441df44295906c8e8ede6bd9df4ff84e0","tid":1378952,"uid":285794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警嘅形象都塑造得差唔多</span></span><br />\n你試下依家隨便落街問人，9成都會話黑警呢樣嗰樣<br />\n然後問繼續上街嘅原因，好多都會話黑警、元朗恐襲、獨立調查委員會，甚至仲有人仍然叫林鄭下台<br />\n<br />\n中共無咩嘢多，就係錢同人多，如果中共突然做以下嘅野：<br />\n1. 表明極反對香港黑警嘅行徑，要重組整個警隊<br />\n(搵幾千人祭旗，私下派安家費)<br />\n2.成立委員會檢討<br />\n(無實質功用，再賴落祭旗嘅人)<br />\n3.林鄭宣佈撤回送中再整個班底問責辭職<br />\n(不必急在一時，換個人就一向都無所謂)<br />\n<br />\n一次回應4個訴求(甚至放哂所有義士)，相信到時會消減到好多怒氣，甚至令國際社會認為香港已經抗爭成功<br />\n然後繼續推智能燈柱，同時全力推大灣區<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到時中共將會更容易控制香港</span></span><br />\n今次收唔返香港，唯有過幾年先再收返香港<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位點睇，始終覺得政府咁努力塑造黑警咁黑，一定有目的<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f6541782949f959e3daa4ad5444e018c0605f5","tid":1378952,"uid":132030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:11:44.000Z","msg":"所以要大家有共識<br />\n5大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n一撚定要有真普選"},{"pid":"73410139e85b3b037fac22d23901e96534b5f7c8","tid":1378952,"uid":285794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:21:59.000Z","msg":"同意，其實無真普選就收得工<br />\n但感覺認知真普選有幾重要嘅仍然唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4baf9704be048df678c06bfc783cb46ab53b15","tid":1378952,"uid":292733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"【 有冇人覺得好無力 ？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378949</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7cf000238e1683f6f9222c88f2b85ae21c9c7f62","tid":1378952,"uid":138296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:26:03.000Z","msg":"佢肯先算 中共"},{"pid":"3dcfc981e2a643cddc7ee67465f56f3e4efc9203","tid":1378952,"uid":16124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:41:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a151686323fc27d0c21bdf0bdabed6598c00468","tid":1378952,"uid":2904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:53:04.000Z","msg":"(集思廣益) 有效應付催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379215</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f4933d9f9852791fffbb93fbb3d059aa2ec2921c","tid":1378952,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:05:44.000Z","msg":"中共好少會讓步"},{"pid":"75c1b0b719855ec0d74ef14ae20766fe0fedca08","tid":1378952,"uid":285794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4933d9f9852791fffbb93fbb3d059aa2ec2921c","tid":1378952,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:05:44.000Z","msg":"中共好少會讓步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"諗諗下又唔一定<br />\n望下嗰d省級領導<br />\n中共只要求其比個罪名再清算<br />\n同一招用落香港都唔出奇"},{"pid":"cf2a2ac3a6a4666b8bd6ae3b750e8106e5758194","tid":1378952,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:32:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">繼續咩都唔做, 慢慢拉晒D前線</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9a18000061ea961c58045c6a5c29ac6bca219910","tid":1378952,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"重啓政改，等香港人下左啖氣，當無事發生。<br />\n等出年立法會選舉後，推一個比8.31<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更緊</span></span>的框架"},{"pid":"7e6acc1c30da3a8193f67ca035ca5434e4b3c761","tid":1378952,"uid":185126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"中共無錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲錢多<br />\n有錢就唔會唔理三峽壩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}